  <h1>Account & Data Deletion Request</h1>

  <p>
    If you would like to delete your <strong>Folks Hub</strong> account and all associated data,
    please follow the instructions below.
  </p>

  <h2>How to request deletion</h2>

  <ul>
    <li>Send an email to: <strong>g.a.t.folkshub.developers@gmail.com</strong></li>
    <li>Use the subject: <strong>Account Deletion Request</strong></li>
    <li>Include your registered email or user ID</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>What will be deleted</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Your profile information</li>
    <li>Your photos</li>
    <li>Your matches and interactions</li>
    <li>Your account data stored in our systems</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Processing time</h2>
  <p>
    Deletion requests are processed within 7–30 days depending on system backups and legal requirements.
  </p>

</body>
